{"type": "article", "id": 36806, "title": "他们的古怪趣味，不仅仅体现在喜欢压扁各种东西上", "description": "唔，你自己看啦。", "date": "2017-01-15T00:15:59Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 36733, "name": "rottingdean"}], "category": 19, "author": 767656, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 94, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170113152314G8BwLmNoh6d5YupU.jpg", "contents": "<p>介绍一对怪诞有趣的伦敦设计师 James Theseus Buck 和 Luke Brooks，他们有一个“品牌” Rottingdean Bazaar，擅长做压扁各种物品的衣服和压扁各种物品的徽章。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170113152716wBsu6KzakOhn5FD0.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.387695\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>&nbsp;James Theseus Buck and Luke Brooks</figcaption> </figure></div><p>气球、花、胡萝卜、酒店拖鞋、袜子、内衣、烟头、茶叶蛋、番茄酱、自己......总之，穿的、用的、玩的、吃的、各种物品都可以压扁，或者装在袋子里压扁。你心里也许会有这样的疑问：“这不是画上去的吗？怎么做到的？”。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170113155000CAZgvOxQpfSY89uE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170113154945C6QoRVhrpDOEwz0G.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170113155020oJsxFbgYPM9dL5vN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.344086\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170113153324HkJnGywAaxrvWR4D.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.304630\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170113153324h2rQ1sICXx48pMfw.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.304630\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201701131533250uB7LiM15GDfUyWd.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.304630\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201701131533252WghloxZGkUNj1yv.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.304630\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170113153246Gaxm7bvjti5d3LcX.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\"> </figure></div><p class=\"\">这正是他们想要的。“我觉得也许因为这些（衣服／徽章上的）东西，你可以很强烈的感受到做这个东西的人和制作过程。我们被太多高完成度和一摸一样的物品所包围，反而很容易忽视这些物品和它们的制作过程。”<a href=\"http://i-d.vice.com/en_us/article/10-things-you-need-to-know-about-londons-newest-design-duo-rottingdean-bazaar\" rel=\"nofollow\">James 对 Vice 解释道。</a>在去年伦敦 Fashion East 男装展示上，他们成功地吸引了人们的注意力。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170113153427Kfw4LekBi78qgl6j.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201701131534277rNVgbiBDIcnflY3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>在形形色色的原材料中，他们最喜欢头发。这可能因为他们两个的毛发都很旺盛…毕竟在中央圣马丁大学（UAL）上同一节课的 Luke 和 James 是因为同为 Julie Verhoeven 的项目 Comfort and Joy 的模特而熟识起来的，那时候 Julie 需要两个毛发旺盛的背。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170113153544EpBtTizkl2U4SXxv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170113153620elZzV8ao4nsC7OAm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><p>这两个人的网站 rottingdeanbazaar.com 上出售部分作品。他们想让 Rottingdean Bazaar 成为一个商店而不是商标或者品牌，这两者的区别是，品牌需要明确的定位和商业计划，而他们只想要一个可以展示和出售自己天马行空想法的商店。</p><p>“我们想要继续保持工作上的自由度，做任何想做的东西，通过任何想要的媒介，和任何组织、个人、表演秀...或者可以在任何时间销售。”<a href=\"http://i-d.vice.com/en_us/article/10-things-you-need-to-know-about-londons-newest-design-duo-rottingdean-bazaar\" rel=\"nofollow\">他们解释道。</a></p><p>除了做压扁各种物品的衣服，Luke 和 James 还与摄影师合作拍摄、策划影像，这俩设计师也经常出现在杂志影像上。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170113153808eaAVIFfbwu5Dhp9J.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.235698\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170113153809EGjRo34SyxmHUBOT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.234286\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170113153809SV4cQevwF25JG936.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.230068\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170113153809Qtew9nck5KOiybmU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.231471\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201701131538094vdH1rxUIyu6CQJ3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.231471\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170113153809Wih5gv8GT6N7Y93K.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.230068\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p>You Smile 《Pylot Magzine》</p></figcaption></figure></div><p>他们不仅有相同的身体特征和品味<a href=\"http://i-d.vice.com/en_us/article/10-things-you-need-to-know-about-londons-newest-design-duo-rottingdean-bazaar\" rel=\"nofollow\">，在形容对方的时候</a>，也表现出一种相同的“不知道是夸奖还是讽刺”的感觉。</p><blockquote>Luke: James很擅长保持一个自然、平静的状态。他很擅长知道什么时候该停下来，比我好太多了。每一天我都特别不想让它结束，感觉要死了一样，但是他喜欢睡觉。</blockquote><blockquote>James：Luke 很擅长挑剔，达到一种强迫的程度，这是一种天赋。主要是因为我在这方面很匮乏。</blockquote><p><a href=\"http://i-d.vice.com/en_us/article/10-things-you-need-to-know-about-londons-newest-design-duo-rottingdean-bazaar\" rel=\"nofollow\">至于朋友们怎么形容他们：</a></p><blockquote>James：像一个秃顶但是多毛的老阿姨。</blockquote><blockquote>Luke: :o</blockquote><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170113154019qeDpId4AVXrGi2fZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.304630\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">Luke</figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201701131540190RBzH9hCqDancbNM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.340628\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">James</figcaption></figure></div><p>题图、文中图来自：Vogue、Rottingdean Bazaar</p>"}